## ğŸ“– Part 4: Deploying a Website for Free  

### ğŸ”¹ **Option 1: GitHub Pages (Best for Static Websites)**  
ğŸ“Œ **Steps to Deploy:**  
1ï¸âƒ£ **Create a GitHub repository** & upload your website files.  
